📚 記憶短文：進擊的管理者 (The Ambitious Administrator)
An ambitious administrator was adept at managing a famous agency. 
Her daily agenda was always full, but she remained accessible to every acquaintance and agent. 
One day, she decided to advocate for an advanced plan to adorn the city’s old buildings.
她是一位有抱負的管理者，熟練於管理一家著名的代理機構。
她的日常議程總是排滿，但她對每一位熟人與代理人都保持易於溝通。
有一天，她決定提倡一項先進的計畫，來裝飾城市的老舊建築。

The administration had to allocate a huge budget for this accomplishment.
Although some felt aback by the absurd cost, the public gave it great acclaim. 
She had to alternate between meetings to affirm that the design was a great alternative to traditional styles.
